2026-04-29T05:35:02.8930052Z 13    <!--
2026-04-29T05:35:02.8931126Z 14        Required for reminders to pop as full-screen notifications over the
2026-04-29T05:35:02.8932430Z 15        lock screen when the user enables "Full-Screen Notifications" in
2026-04-29T05:35:02.8934068Z 16        Settings → Notifications. Android 14+ restricts this to apps whose
2026-04-29T05:35:02.8948117Z 17        core function is alarms/calendar/communication; for other apps the
2026-04-29T05:35:02.8949998Z 18        system downgrades it to a heads-up notification, which is fine —
