2026-04-29T05:35:02.8955381Z 21-->/home/runner/work/prismTask/prismTask/app/src/main/AndroidManifest.xml:16:22-78
2026-04-29T05:35:02.8956704Z 22    <!--
2026-04-29T05:35:02.8957521Z 23        Exact alarm permissions. We request both so reminders fire reliably
2026-04-29T05:35:02.8958458Z 24        across Android versions:
2026-04-29T05:35:02.8959697Z 25          - SCHEDULE_EXACT_ALARM: required on Android 12 (API 31-32); the
2026-04-29T05:35:02.8960761Z 26            user must toggle it on via Settings. We prompt for this in
2026-04-29T05:35:02.8961806Z 27            MainActivity when canScheduleExactAlarms() returns false.
2026-04-29T05:35:02.8962845Z 28          - USE_EXACT_ALARM: auto-granted on Android 13+ (API 33+) for
2026-04-29T05:35:02.8963879Z 29            calendar/reminder/timer-style apps, so no prompt is needed.
2026-04-29T05:35:02.8964930Z 30        Without USE_EXACT_ALARM the app was silently falling back to
2026-04-29T05:35:02.8966492Z 31        inexact alarms on Android 13+, which Samsung (and other OEMs)
2026-04-29T05:35:02.8967491Z 32        aggressively delay or drop under Doze/App Standby.
2026-04-29T05:35:02.8968293Z 33    -->
2026-04-29T05:35:02.8969353Z 34    <uses-permission android:name="android.permission.SCHEDULE_EXACT_ALARM" />
